    caption: [Types of tissues in a vertebrate (frog). Epithelial tissues (e.g., columnar in intestine, stratified in epidermis). Connective tissues (e.g., bone, blood, areolar). Muscle tissues (e.g., cardiac, smooth, skeletal). Nervous tissues (e.g., in brain).],
